{"title":"伏汛时节","authors":["牛雅杰"],"dates":[{"year":1998,"month":7,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏汛时节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛雅杰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏雨时节，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天似漏斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩浩山洪震吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滔滔白浪滚球。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备好了吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"应有尽有。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍是英雄的时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"考验正是时候！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"险情在面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安全在身后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身前大河激流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身后大街人流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大堤踩在脚下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"责任扛在肩头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千躯易得，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百勇难求，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平时惜命如金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"关键时不畏虎口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑影里有人在呼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪电中众声答“有”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看伏汛过后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金堤塑像千秋。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}